      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for checking out my car! I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it\u2019s been incredibly reliable for everything from grocery runs to weekend getaways. It\u2019s in really nice shape and drives super smoothly\u2014you can tell it\u2019s been well-cared for! It has a few minor bits of wear here and there from normal use, but it's honestly a fantastic, solid ride that's ready for its next adventure. I\u2019m looking for a quick, easy sale, so feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
