    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 inline-six engine. This unit retains its high-revving character with crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. Mechanical maintenance is up to date, including a proactive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement\u2014essential for long-term chassis rigidity. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the communicative steering feel these cars are known for.",
